name: RPK Discount Luggage Superstore, Inc.
overview: Whatever kind of luggage you are looking for, RPK Luggage Online, Inc. stocks it. Choose bags from a number of popular brands available for men, women, and kids. We carry a wide range of bags and other types of luggage such as backpacks, briefcases, duffels, handbags, luggage sets, pet carriers, sling bags, wallets, wheeled bags and many more. Tanya Johns, owner of RPKluggageOnline.com, is an accountant who enjoys going on leisure trips and buying souvenirs from all over the country. She likes to collect all kinds of keychains and her collections, which she started while still in college, now amounts to almost a hundred and is still growing. Tanya is a self-confessed movie fanatic and is a sucker for romantic comedies. She also loves shopping and is always on the lookout for great bargains.
